            <h2 class="text-center">Donation &amp; Scholarship</h2>
<p>Bruzoo is a non-profit organization, and it helps those children who despite being talented are not able to show their talent due to paucity of money, so we Bruzoo work to improve their versatility, and we bear the full cost of their education for a complete one year. We bear the cost so that those children never have to think about how they will pay fees or any expenses related to their education, we take all their worries on ourselves and at the same time, for the children who are weak with money, we take care of their food and drink and most take care of their health.</p>
<p>In this noble cause, we spend our whole life so that the future of the children can be made bright. Therefore, whoever will give us their support in this noble work, we will get more strength, and we will be able to contribute more and more for the quality education and overall development of more and more children, so all of you contribute to this good work. We present our gratitude on behalf of all the children for all of them and wish that you also touch the heights of success so that you too can contribute more and more noble work towards the welfare of society.</p>
<p>We do the hiring of teachers so that children can be given a good future and at the same time we have collaboration with many schools, and we do not have any fees of any kind, nor registration or any kind of course fee.
Likewise, we provide scholarships to the children which depend on their performance in the exam taken by us. Likewise, we take this exam every month, whose fee is a maximum of 10 rupees, which is decided by the management whether to take this fee or not and the children who pass are given scholarships by us. We do not provide any kind, of course, we just provide good education facilities to the children</p>

